#~ "compile_kde3_2.html\"> Compiling &kde; 3.2.x</ulink>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you cannot obtain a suitable precompiled binary package, you need to "
#~ "compile &konsolekalendar; yourself from source files. Get the source "
#~ "package file <filename>kdepim-x.x.tar.bz2</filename>. Unpack it in a new "
#~ "folder using a command similar to <userinput><command>tar</command> "
#~ "<option>xvfj <replaceable>package.tar.bz2</replaceable></option></"
#~ "userinput>, and change to the folder which has been created."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui sul ei õnnestu hankida sobivat eelnevalt kompileeritud binaarpaketti, "
#~ "tuleb &konsolekalendar; lähtetekstist ise kompileerida. Hangi lähtepakett "
#~ "<filename>kdepim-x.x.tar.bz2</filename>. Paki see lahti uude kataloogi "
#~ "käsuga <userinput><command>tar</command> <option>xvfj <replaceable>pakett."
#~ "tar.bz2</replaceable></option></userinput> ja liigu loodud kataloogi."

#~ msgid "&install.compile.documentation;"
#~ msgstr "&install.compile.documentation;"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "If you have more than one version of &kde; installed (e.g. &kde;2 and "
#~ "&kde;3), this may possibly install &konsolekalendar; into the wrong &kde; "
#~ "folder. If necessary, you can give the &kde; folder as a parameter to "
#~ "<userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>. For example, if "
#~ "your &kde; is installed in <filename>/opt/kde3</filename>:"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Kui paigaldatud on enam kui üks &kde; versioon (nt. &kde;2 ja &kde;3), "
#~ "võib juhtuda, et paigaldad &konsolekalendar;i valesse &kde; kataloogi. "
#~ "Vajadusel anna &kde; kataloog parameetrina käsule <userinput><command>./"
#~ "configure</command></userinput>. Kui näiteks &kde; on paigaldatud "
#~ "kataloogi <filename>/opt/kde3</filename>:"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "<command>./configure</command> --prefix=<replaceable>/opt/kde3</"
#~ "replaceable>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "<command>./configure</command> --prefix=<replaceable>/opt/kde3</"
#~ "replaceable>"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The current version of &konsolekalendar; does not support inserting "
#~ "<quote>free</quote> events (free events are events that take up no space "
#~ "in the day; &ie;, the time is not marked as busy). Birthdays, holidays, "
#~ "anniversaries, &etc; should ideally be inserted as free events. We hope "
#~ "for the next &konsolekalendar; release to have a <quote>free</quote> "
#~ "event feature."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "&konsolekalendar;i praegune versioon ei toeta <quote>vabade</quote> "
#~ "sündmuste lisamist (vabad sündmused on sellised, mis ei võta päevas "
#~ "ruumi, &ie; toimuvad ajal, mis ei ole märgitud hõivatuks). Sünnipäevad, "
#~ "pühad, aastapäevad &etc; sobivad ideaalselt vabadeks sündmusteks. Me "
#~ "loodame, et juba järgmises &konsolekalendar;i versioonis on ka võimalus "
#~ "lisada <quote>vabu</quote> sündmusi."
